Invocation Name: super tech support
des:
Super Tech Support is here to solve any technical issues you have, at all, with anything. Really. We have a solution to everything! Just tell us the issue you are having, and we will impart to you our words of wisdom.

(Please note that if the suggested solution does not in fact solve your problem, then it is entirely your fault for believing it would in the first place.)
